Open file <code>/usr/local/etc/torrc.d/50_user.conf</code> in a [https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Software#Text_Editor text editor] of your choice, with administrative rights. For example, we recommend you use <code>sudoedit</code>.

{{Box|text=
<u>If you are using [[Qubes|{{q_project_name_long}}]]</u>, take the following step.

<code>Qubes App Launcher (blue/grey "Q")</code> &rarr; <code>{{project_name_gateway_long}} ProxyVM (commonly named {{project_name_gateway_vm}})</code> &rarr; <code>Tor User Config (Torrc)</code>

<u>If you are using a graphical {{project_name_gateway_short}}</u>, take the following step.

<code>Start Menu</code> &rarr; <code>Applications</code> &rarr; <code>Settings</code> &rarr; <code>/usr/local/etc/torrc.d/50_user.conf
</code>

<u>If you are using a terminal-only {{project_name_gateway_short}}</u>, take the following step.
